title: Onii-chan Datte Amaetai Wake de
description: Boyish Kanata is always taken advantage of by his younger brother, Keita. To relieve his stress, Kanata works at a cafe where men pay for young guys to act as their little brothers. It's a great job, until Keita finds out about it...!
